<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shòu xǐ guī rù yé sū jī dū 迦南1183</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shòu xǐ guī rù yé sū jī dū, tiān fù huān xǐ tiān shǐ huān hū.
 chéng wèi xīn rén xíng zǒu tiān lù, míng zì qiān rù zhǔ de guó dù.
 hā lì lù yà wǒ zhēn yǒu fú hā lì lù yà wǒ zhēn yǒu fú.
 hā lì lù yà wǒ zhēn yǒu fú shì yīn jiù zhǔ yé sū jī dū.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1183</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>